attributes.title: Don’t Download this App!!!
attributes.review: This app took forever to download! I, a very active cult mem- fan of Donny, wanted to download this app but it took 4 days and it just now finished! When it did, my phone, laptop, IPad, and tv started freaking out! All of my electronics were frozen and then a notification popped up on all the screens asking many different personal questions. I was very confused. Then I look to my laptop and see that it started recording! Mind you, I was nowhere near it and it had been shut down all day! I feel so uncomfortable and afraid. The app actually hacked into all of my devices and who knows if it was downloading personal data 😱 I very highly do not recommend you download this app!
